344
00:31:33,472 --> 00:31:36,254
That was a consideration for time and money.

345
00:31:37,295 --> 00:31:46,382
Another consideration was to construct a separate utility bridge prefabricated steel truss immediately east of the existing bridge.

346
00:31:46,502 --> 00:32:00,553
